<body>
    <noscript>
        <iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-MZ3QLZZ" height=0 width=0
                style=display:none;visibility:hidden></iframe>
    </noscript>
    <noscript>
        <strong>
            We're sorry but mask-map doesn't work properly without JavaScript enabled. Please enable it to
            continue.
        </strong>
    </noscript>
    <div class="info" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#divInfo">
        <h1>口罩供需資訊平台 & 健保特約醫事機構地圖</h1>
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="modal fade" id="divInfo" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="網站聲明" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title">網站聲明</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>您好：</p>
                    <p>口罩的取得須依政府頒布的規則辦理。 庫存數量僅供參考，資訊約每十分鐘更新一次，實際庫存仍以個別單位現場為準。</p>
                    <p>
                        詳細情況以 <a target="_blank" href="https://www.nhi.gov.tw/Content_List.aspx?n=395F52D193F3B5C7&topn=787128DAD5F71B1A">衛生福利部中央健康保險署</a> 說明為主
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        網頁資料由 <a target="_blank" href="https://mask.pdis.nat.gov.tw/">口罩供需資訊平台</a> 與社群朋友提供，感謝各方協助。
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        本網頁是<del>根本就是 95%抄襲</del>致敬 <a target="_blank" href="https://kuro.tw/mask-map/"> kuro_mask-map</a>、 
                        <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/kurotanshi/mask-map"> Github開源</a>，藉此練 Leaflet.js。感謝 Kuro、讚嘆 Kuro。
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lmask"></div>
    <div id="map"></div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-CSXorXvZcTkaix6Yvo6HppcZGetbYMGWSFlBw8HfCJo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.6.0/leaflet-src.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/leaflet/1.6.0/leaflet-src.js.map"></script>
